(start with my last post) Ares made a mistake turning to fight Shadow 
wing, his counter attack left him open to Lunarpine, Lunarpine lands 
a shoulder tackle pushing Ares back, lunarpine continues attacking 
with claws slashing, first at Ares arms, then at his torso.

"Thanks for the assist wing now get out of the line of fire and let 
me handle this piece of slag." 

He could see she was hurting and any more abuse could cause some 
permanent damage. She wouldn't take any more damage if he had 
anything to say about it. Lunarpine had a promise to keep and this 
lambchop wasn't going to make him break it.
